          <div class="col-md-6" style= "padding: 4%">
          <p>In this decade, the public has also realized that traditional chemical solutions to health problems are themselves health risks.
            The FDA banned 19 of the 21 active ingredients in anti-bacterial products currently available. These product include Wet Ones wipes,
