            providing a superior service using advanced technology.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row" >
          <div class="col-md-6" style= "padding: 4%">
          <p>UVC Tech seeks to revolutionize preventive healthcare by adding UV-C-LED antibacterial technologies to everyday items that we all
            touch. This “add-on” initiative does not require changing existing material or equipment, saving on time and costs; whilst allowing
            for universal acceptance wherever UVC Tech can be used to make our community a healthier, safer place.
          </p>
        </div>
